tableInfo.caption: 关联标准
tableInfo.sql: SELECT A.DWID,A.JX,A.JH,B.MC JXMC,C.MC JHMC,D.MC JLDW,A.BZSL,A.KCSL,CASE WHEN BZSL=0 THEN '非标准' WHEN BZSL>0 AND BZSL < KCSL THEN '超出标准' when BZSL >0 AND BZSL > KCSL THEN '不足标准' when BZSL>0 AND BZSL=KCSL THEN '=标准' else ''end bz FROM (SELECT A.DWID,A.JX,A.JH,A.SL BZSL,NVL(CK.SL,0) KCSL FROM T_ZB_BZ A LEFT JOIN V_CK_ZB CK ON A.JX=CK.JX AND A.JH=CK.JH UNION SELECT DWID,A.JX,A.JH,0 BZSL,A.SL KCSL FROM V_CK_ZB A WHERE (JX,JH)NOT IN (SELECT JX,JH FROM T_ZB_BZ) )A LEFT JOIN T_JH_JX B ON A.JX=B.ID LEFT JOIN T_JH_JH C ON A.JH=C.ID LEFT JOIN T_XT_JLDW D ON C.DW=D.ID LEFT JOIN V_CK_ZB CK ON A.JX=CK.JX AND A.JH=CK.JH WHERE 1=1 ORDER BY A.BZSL,A.JX,A.JH

tableInfo.caption: 战备库存信息
tableInfo.sql: select T_JH_JX.MC JXMC,T_JH_JH.MC JHMC,T_XT_JLDW.MC JLDW,to_char(YSRQ,'YYYY-MM-DD') YSRQR,ZSMXS-nvl(ZFXXS,0) SYXS,to_char(RKRQ,'YYYY-MM-DD')RKRQR, to_char(YFRQ,'YYYY-MM-DD')YFRQR,TO_Char(ADD_MONTHS(YFRQ,12*YFQX),'YYYY-MM-DD')YFQZ, T_JH_ZL.mc ZLMC,T_QX_DW.JM CKMC,T_XT_HCLB.MC HCLBMC, A.DJ DJG,A.DJ*A.SL ZJG,T_XT_BZLB.HL NEWHL,T_XT_BZLB.MC BZMC, ZSMN ZSMNN, DJ*A.HL YHLDJ,DJ*A.HL*A.SL YHLZJ,DJ*T_XT_BZLB.HL XHLDJ,DJ*T_XT_BZLB.HL*A.SL XHLZJ, A.* from T_CK_CK A left join T_JH_JH on T_JH_JH.ID=JH LEFT JOIN T_XT_JLDW ON T_XT_JLDW.ID=T_JH_JH.DW left join T_JH_JX on T_JH_JX.id=A.jx left join T_JH_ZL on T_JH_ZL.id=zl left join T_QX_DW on T_QX_DW.ID=CKDM left join T_XT_HCLB ON T_XT_HCLB.ID=A.HCLB LEFT JOIN T_XT_BZLB ON T_XT_BZLB.ID=A.BBZ where 1=1 AND QCLB=2 and A.SL>0 ORDER BY A.JX,A.JH

tableInfo.sql: select T_QX_DW.MC As DRDWMC,T_CK_CRKQD.BH,T_CK_CRKQD.CKDM,T_CK_CRKQD.JWH,T_CK_CRKQD.JX,T_CK_CRKQD.FJH,T_CK_CRKQD.JH,T_CK_CRKQD.XH,T_CK_CRKQD.TZS,T_CK_CRKQD.ZL,T_CK_CRKQD.DJ,T_CK_CRKQD.ZJ,T_CK_CRKQD.CCRQ,T_CK_CRKQD.YSRQ,T_CK_CRKQD.SMZT,T_CK_CRKQD.RKRQ,T_CK_CRKQD.ZSMN,T_CK_CRKQD.ZSMXS,T_CK_CRKQD.ZSMXH,T_CK_CRKQD.ZSMQL,T_CK_CRKQD.ZFXCS,T_CK_CRKQD.YFRQ,T_CK_CRKQD.FXRQ,T_CK_CRKQD.FXSMN,T_CK_CRKQD.FXSMXS,T_CK_CRKQD.FXCS,T_CK_CRKQD.SBQXN,T_CK_CRKQD.SBQXXS,T_CK_CRKQD.BZ,T_CK_CRKQD.ZFXXS,T_CK_CRKQD.BCZFXXS,T_CK_CRKQD.BCFXXS,T_CK_CRKQD.ZXHCS,T_CK_CRKQD.BCZXHCS,T_CK_CRKQD.BCXHCS,T_CK_CRKQD.ZQLCS,T_CK_CRKQD.BCZQLCS,T_CK_CRKQD.BCQLCS,T_CK_CRKQD.DBBZ,T_CK_CRKQD.CJRQ,T_CK_CRKQD.YFCS,T_CK_CRKQD.ZYFCS,T_CK_CRKQD.XSBZ,T_CK_CRKQD.XZ,T_CK_CRKQD.HL,T_CK_CRKQD.DWID,T_CK_CRKQD.LB,T_CK_CRKQD.RQ,T_CK_CRKQD.CXSGIN,T_CK_CRKQD.JJ,T_CK_CRKQD.HCLB,T_CK_CRKQD.ZYLB,T_CK_CRKQD.YXH,T_CK_CRKQD.ZGQCS,T_CK_CRKQD.GQCS,T_CK_CRKQD.YFQX,T_CK_CRKQD.FKLB,T_CK_CRKQD.JJS,T_CK_CRKQD.ZDDM,T_CK_CRKQD.SJS,T_CK_CRKQD.JXQN,T_CK_CRKQD.JXQXS,T_CK_CRKQD.RFID,T_CK_CRKQD.YSID,T_CK_CRKQD.YJH,T_CK_CRKQD.XFRQ,T_CK_DBQD.DCdw,T_CK_DBQD.DRDW,T_CK_DBQD.SQD,T_CK_DBQD.Sl,T_CK_DBQD.DBDH,T_CK_DBQD.DBR, T_JH_ZL.Mc AS ZLMC,T_JH_JX.MC as JXMC,T_CK_DBQD.BBZ,T_XT_BZLB.mc as BZMC,T_XT_HCLB.mc as hclbmc,T_JH.MC JHMC,T_XT_JLDW.MC JLDW,ADD_MONTHS(T_CK_DBQD.YFRQ,12*T_CK_DBQD.YFQX) YFQZ,T_CK_DBQD.Sl KCSL,T_CK_DBQD.BH DXBH from T_CK_CRKQD left join T_CK_DBQD on T_CK_DBQD.Bh =T_CK_CRKQD.Bh and T_CK_DBQD.Jh=T_CK_CRKQD.jh and T_CK_DBQD.Xh=T_CK_DBQD.xh left join T_JH_ZL on T_JH_ZL.ID =T_CK_CRKQD.Zl left join T_JH_JX on T_JH_JX.id = T_CK_CRKQD.JX left join T_QX_DW on T_QX_DW.id=T_CK_DBQD.DRDW left join T_XT_BZLB on T_XT_BZLB.id=T_CK_DBQD.BBZ left join T_XT_HCLB on T_XT_HCLB.id=T_CK_CRKQD.Hclb LEFT JOIN T_JH ON T_JH.ID=T_CK_CRKQD.JH LEFT JOIN T_XT_JLDW ON T_XT_JLDW.ID=T_JH.DW where 1=1
